In a large microwave safe bowl, heat margarine and marshmallows at HIGH for 3 minutes, stirring after 2 minutes. Stir in vanilla. Stir in KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal until well coated. When slightly cooled, shape mixture into 12 candy shapes using buttered hands. Place on surface sprayed with cooking spray, or wax paper and refrigerate. In a small sauce pan over low heat, melt chocolate and shortening. Stir until smooth. Dip each candy cane into the melted white chocolate and refrigerate on a flat surface to cool. Best if served same day.